@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us";
}

<div class="container">
    <h2 class="display-4 text-center">About Our Book Store</h2>

    <p class="lead text-center">
        Welcome to our Book Store! We are dedicated to providing a wide variety of books across different genres.
    </p>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/images/6846452.jpg" alt="Bookshelf" class="img-fluid mb-4" style="max-width: 90%;" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>
                Whether you are looking for fiction, non-fiction, academic resources, or children's books, we have something
                for every reader. Our collection is carefully curated to ensure that you find the best reads at affordable
                prices. We work hard to maintain a diverse inventory, featuring both bestsellers and hidden gems.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="mt-5">Our Mission</h3>
    <p>
        Our mission is to foster a love for reading and to make books accessible to everyone. We believe that books
        have the power to inspire, educate, and entertain. Our goal is to connect readers with the stories and
        information they seek. We also aim to support local authors and promote regional literature, enriching our community
        with unique voices and perspectives.
    </p>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>
                At our store, you can find not just books but also a warm and welcoming atmosphere where you can spend
                hours browsing. Our knowledgeable staff is always on hand to recommend titles and help you find exactly what you’re looking for.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/images/24307396_6920933.jpg" alt="Reading Area" class="img-fluid mb-4" style="max-width: 90%;" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
    <p>
        We believe in giving back to the community. Our store regularly hosts events, including author signings, book clubs, and reading sessions for children.
        These initiatives are designed to bring people together, foster discussions about literature, and create a vibrant community of readers.
    </p>

    <h3>Thank You for Visiting!</h3>
    <p>
        Thank you for visiting our store, and we hope you find your next favorite book with us! We invite you to explore our selection, join our events,
        and become part of our reading community.
    </p>
</div>
